{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id9c39f282-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7","identifier":"/us/usc/t8/s1324d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1324d"},"text":"§ 1324d.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Civil penalties for failure to depart","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id9c39f283-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7","identifier":"/us/usc/t8/s1324d/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Any alien subject to a final order of removal who—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id9c39f284-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7","identifier":"/us/usc/t8/s1324d/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" willfully fails or refuses to—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id9c39f285-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7","identifier":"/us/usc/t8/s1324d/a/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" depart from the United States pursuant to the order,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id9c39f286-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7","identifier":"/us/usc/t8/s1324d/a/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" make timely application in good faith for travel or other documents necessary for departure, or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id9c39f287-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7","identifier":"/us/usc/t8/s1324d/a/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" present for removal at the time and place required by the Attorney General; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id9c39f288-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7","identifier":"/us/usc/t8/s1324d/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" conspires to or takes any action designed to prevent or hamper the alien’s departure pursuant to the order,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"shall pay a civil penalty of not more than $500 to the Commissioner for each day the alien is in violation of this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id9c39f289-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7","identifier":"/us/usc/t8/s1324d/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Construction","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Nothing in this section shall be construed to diminish or qualify any penalties to which an alien may be subject for activities proscribed by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1253/a"},"text":"section 1253(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":" or any other section of this chapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id9c39f28a-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1952-06-27/ch477"},"text":"June 27, 1952, ch. 477","children":[],"tail":", title II, ch. 8, § 274D, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/208/dC/tIII/s380/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–208, div. C, title III, § 380(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-09-30"},"text":"Sept. 30, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/3009-650"},"text":"110 Stat. 3009–650","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id9c39f28b-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id9c39f28c-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id9c39f28d-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in subsec. (b), was in the original, “this Act”, meaning ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1952-06-27/ch477"},"text":"act June 27, 1952, ch. 477","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/66/163"},"text":"66 Stat. 163","children":[],"tail":", known as the Immigration and Nationality Act, which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1101"},"text":"section 1101 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id9c39f28e-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"id9c39f28f-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/208/dC/tIII/s380/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–208, div. C, title III, § 380(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-09-30"},"text":"Sept. 30, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/3009-650"},"text":"110 Stat. 3009–650","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/104/208/dC/tIII/s380/c"},"text":"“The amendment made by subsection (a) [enacting this section] shall apply to actions occurring on or after the title III–A effective date (as defined in section 309(a) of this division [set out as a note under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1101"},"text":"section 1101 of this title","children":[],"tail":"]).”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id9c39f290-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Abolition of Immigration and Naturalization Service and Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For abolition of Immigration and Naturalization Service, transfer of functions, and treatment of related references, see note set out under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1551"},"text":"section 1551 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id9c39f291-3a6f-11f1-ace3-bb5201d4c7c7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References to Order of Removal Deemed To Include Order of Exclusion and Deportation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of carrying out this chapter, any reference in law to an order of removal is deemed to include a reference to an order of exclusion and deportation or an order of deportation, see ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/208/s309/d/2"},"text":"section 309(d)(2) of Pub. L. 104–208","children":[],"tail":", set out in an Effective Date of 1996 Amendments note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1101"},"text":"section 1101 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
